Task 1: Basic Text Classification
Build a simple text classification model and compare 2–3 algorithms.
Dataset Used- 20 Newsgroups Dataset (Binary Classification)
Models Used-
- Naive Bayes
- Logistic Regression
- Support Vector Machine (SVM)
Evaluation Metrics-
- Accuracy Score
- Confusion Matrix
- Classification Report


Task 2: Word Embedding Mini Task
Model Used- GloVe (glove-wiki-gigaword-50)
Tasks Completed- 
- Loaded pretrained embedding model
- Found similar words (e.g., king → queen)
- Performed analogy (king - man + woman)
- Visualized 10 words using PCA (2D plot)


Task 3: Mini NLP Application-  Fake News Detection System
Classify news as Fake or Real.
Method Used-
- Text Cleaning
- TF-IDF Vectorization
- Logistic Regression Model
Evaluation-
- Accuracy Score
- Confusion Matrix
- Classification Report
- Top important words displayed
